data.title: List of Designated Persons, Groups & Entities Under Paragraph 4 (2) of The United Nations Regulations No. 1 of 2012
data.meta_description: List of Designated persons, groups & entities under paragraph 4(2) of the United Nations Regulations No. 1 of 2012 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is a Gazette Extraordinary from the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka dated March 21, 2014. It contains listings of designated persons, groups and entities under the United Nations Regulations No. 1 of 2012. There are schedules listing 16 entities and 13 individuals that have been designated and are subject to sanctions. The listings include organizations such as the Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam (LTTE) and individuals living in countries like Australia, Belgium and Canada.
